==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Perpetually
<hw>Per*pet"u*al*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In a perpetual manner; constantly; continually.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The Bible and Common Prayer Book in the vulgar tongue, being <qex>perpetually</qex> read in churches, have proved a kind of standard for language.</q>
<au>Swift.</au>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Perpetualty</ent>⟦br⟧
